{"id": "1504887714749874326", "channel_id": "1504887714749874326", "type": 0, "author_id": "185935184439410688", "author_name": "mirrorsara", "author_bot": false, "content": "The upcoming anniversary reruns only lasting for one day is a really bad design for new players, for a lot of reasons.\n\n1. Older players know which reruns they want to pull for, new players don't. With only one day to pull on a character there's no time for new players to get advice from the community, and even after making the choice to pull they won't have the savings of an older player and may have to rush to earn as much as they can before their desired banner ends. Players also might start partway through the patch when the collab event starts, or as word of mouth spreads news about the anniversary, meaning they'll miss many of the reruns.\n\n2. On the same note, Ethereal Core rewards aren't all given out on day 1, the banners start with older units but there's still a chance you may not earn all the cores by the time a specific banner arrives.\n\n3. As has been mentioned elsewhere, the combined wheel+awakener banners make it difficult to target what you want, and BIAV already acknowledged and apologized for this as a design mistake in version 2.4. Doing the same thing after previously issuing an apology makes the apology look like a lie to appease upset players rather than an actual admission of a mistake.", "timestamp": "2026-05-15T16:46:30.658000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👆", "emoji_id": null, "count": 13}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1504887714749874326", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "One Day Rerun Banners", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"], "is_thread_starter": true}
