{"id": "1504897469677306057", "channel_id": "1504887714749874326", "type": 19, "author_id": "231543819026300928", "author_name": "crowlov1", "author_bot": false, "content": "On second ani.\nThere were 8 arc2 units reruns.\nDaily and they were rotating so on day 1 was for example GDoll and it would continue to swap every day, until you reach day 9 where it was GDoll again.\n\nThis half ani is this but on a much much bigger scale.", "timestamp": "2026-05-15T17:25:16.414000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["774105235572260864"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1504893456097738952", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1504887714749874326", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "One Day Rerun Banners", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
