{"id": "1504902085836144702", "channel_id": "1504887714749874326", "type": 0, "author_id": "185935184439410688", "author_name": "mirrorsara", "author_bot": false, "content": "On 3, if the banners have no other SSR content on them at all you're not wrong. But their description specifies the guarantee is after getting two *limited* SSRs of one type. If there are still standard items in the pool then the banners just aren't good. If it only takes 90 pulls max to get at least one copy of the character and wheel that's not bad, but I'm not alone in assuming you won't be guaranteed a featured item every 30 pulls. It still makes pulling Enlightens/OE awkward if you get too many wheels since Awakener dupes after e3 are a lot more valuable than Wheel dupes after w3, but that's not as big of an issue.\n\nHonestly the main reason I made this post is the one day rotation though. New players just don't have time to figure out if they want or should pull for a daily character until the next one replaces them, and with this many I don't see them rotating more than once.", "timestamp": "2026-05-15T17:43:36.992000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1504887714749874326", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "One Day Rerun Banners", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1504910241656082625", "channel_id": "1504887714749874326", "type": 0, "author_id": "185935184439410688", "author_name": "mirrorsara", "author_bot": false, "content": "although, if it's 33/66 character/wheel like the Kaleido banner then it's still not great even with only the two items in the pool, especially if you're trying to pull lots of characters you don't have and don't want every single wheel", "timestamp": "2026-05-15T18:16:01.491000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1504887714749874326", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "One Day Rerun Banners", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1504919539484332052", "channel_id": "1504887714749874326", "type": 0, "author_id": "185935184439410688", "author_name": "mirrorsara", "author_bot": false, "content": "and as Lens pointed out with some math elsewhere, because the Wheel guarantee can kick in to keep you from getting too many characters in a row, the average pulls per character is higher than it would be on a regular banner where the guarantee only increases your odds instead of averaging them", "timestamp": "2026-05-15T18:52:58.266000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "💯", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1504887714749874326", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "One Day Rerun Banners", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
